    "description": "“取货点模拟器 ”是一款第一人称模拟器，在这款模拟器中，您将遇到在取货点工作的所有复杂情况。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/724e15f3f523b47d4523207ed6678a07.avif?t=1744131756\" width=800 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/b6934b305c50864d072d5a6007e11af9.poster.avif?t=1744131756\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/b6934b305c50864d072d5a6007e11af9.webm?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/b6934b305c50864d072d5a6007e11af9.mp4?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>注意内部设计，影响其舒适度和效率。您将决定您的提货点的外观，顾客会欣赏您的想法并留下反馈意见。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/7230b146c7ac91f9ac7df90d24d5d143.avif?t=1744131756\" width=669 height=91 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/e9cf672991216754826233e3c022fa91.poster.avif?t=1744131756\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/e9cf672991216754826233e3c022fa91.webm?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/e9cf672991216754826233e3c022fa91.mp4?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您必须按时订购货物，并确保您的仓库总是满满的。至于选择什么类别的货物--这取决于您。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/d2575877e18cf75ec66f91b153a04ae8.avif?t=1744131756\" width=652 height=91 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/98477894a7a7bdb176fcef999335299a.poster.avif?t=1744131756\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/98477894a7a7bdb176fcef999335299a.webm?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/98477894a7a7bdb176fcef999335299a.mp4?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>扫描二维码，找到合适的产品，将其交给客户，同时不要忘记确保客户满意。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/6ab0c6658a19f5a3a413c56933fd4cf8.avif?t=1744131756\" width=753 height=91 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/051490cc810ae386de4c032d1f478203.poster.avif?t=1744131756\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/051490cc810ae386de4c032d1f478203.webm?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316030/extras/051490cc810ae386de4c032d1f478203.mp4?t=1744131756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>不仅要升级您的取货点，还要升级您自己：通过学习技能开启新机遇，创建您附近最成功的企业。",
